{"tid":920621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台選後美軍艦通過台灣海峽　五角大廈：展現美方承諾","createTime":"2018-11-29T03:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T07:51:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"873ac7b66fbe546f802403482cb1118ca212f73a","tid":920621,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:02:17.000Z","msg":"建立時間：2018/11/29 08:54<br />\n台灣國防部昨日昨日表示，美軍兩艘軍艦於昨日晨間通過台灣海峽。美國五角大廈及第七艦隊隨後發聲明證明此事，強調美國藉此展現對「自由與開放的印太」的承諾。<br />\n根據台灣國防部，美軍一艘作戰艦、一艘補給艦28日清晨從台灣東北部海域進入台灣海峽、向西南航行，當晚脫離台灣海峽。這是美國軍艦今年第三度通過台灣海峽。五角大廈發言人羅根（Christopher Logan）昨日證實，美國導向飛彈驅逐艦史托克代爾號（USS Stockdale, DDG 106）及油料補給艦貝科斯號（USNS Pecos, T-AO-197）「例行性通過台灣海峽」。<br />\n中央社報導指出，對於美國軍艦這次為何選擇台海這一水域、在這一時間點通過，羅根僅表示，美軍兩艘軍艦行經台海，符合國際法規範，這展現美國對「自由與開放的印太」的承諾。另據路透，美國海軍太平洋艦隊也發表聲明證實此事，強調美軍未來將持續在國際法允許地區內執行飛航及航海活動。<br />\n路透同時分析，美軍此時再度派軍艦通過台灣海峽，恐怕將加深美中之間的緊張關係。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181129/1475258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181129%2F1475258&d=U0Pt4ZSIax%2BM6%2FJa6Mfzr8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=39b1ee6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181129%2F1475258&h=ada79eaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181129/1475258</a>"},{"pid":"8ba831c1eba7cab5e7dfe6a0742bf3743b52d64e","tid":920621,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:04:20.000Z","msg":"牙侵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5d6b67a46cc5f3cca1e2f6dd03d25a0a50fea","tid":920621,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:04:58.000Z","msg":"明顯俾壓力支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefb733b6be837c77014f88a62d4d3e153fd0d1a","tid":920621,"uid":33099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T03:07:18.000Z","msg":"D 台仔蠢到死<br />\n<br />\n美國分明俾位你上自己都唔珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48440510e5be6d7c54bbaf58ade2fa19ac05716","tid":920621,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"台灣人是扶不起的柯斗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}